title: Rangers leaning on Hamels again in ALDS Game 5 at Toronto
text:
> Texas Rangers leaning on Hamels again in ALDS Game 5 at Toronto Texas Rangers manager Jeff Banister smiles as he listens to a question during a news conference Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015, in Arlington, Texas. The Rangers will play the Toronto Blue Jays Wednesday in Toronto in Game 5 of the baseball's ALDS. (AP Photo/Tony Gutierrez) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
